Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/hhu-stups/tlc4b
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: tlc4b
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre-headless | java-runtime-headless, ${misc:Depends}
Description: model-check classical B specifications with TLA+/TLC
 TLC4B translates a classical B specification to TLA+, runs the TLC model
 checker on the result, and translates any counterexample found back to the B
 level so it can be inspected in terms of the original model.
 .
 This package installs the TLC4B jar together with its runtime dependencies and
 a "tlc4b" launcher.
